name: Kim Jung-Gi Style V1
description:
Appreciate my work? Can you buy me a coffe please :)

This model is inspired by and in memory of the legendary master of perspective, drawing and scketh and unrivaled imagination, who I greatly admire for creating such incredible intricate and detailed scenes I have seen so far.

This is the first version of the Kim Jung-Gi style, which I consider still does not reach the great style and beauty of his works, but it is a little closer to that greatness.

I hope many of you like such a style of the great master that has come before us but that inspires this model of his great art.

QR to my page buymeacoffee
